Package: AzureGraph
Title: Simple interface to 'Microsoft Graph'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hong", "Ooi", , "hongooi@microsoft.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Microsoft", role="cph")
    )
Description: A simple R interface to 'Graph', the API framework for accessing data in Microsoft's various online services. It currently includes functionality to manage 'Azure Active Directory' objects, with a view to enhancing R interoperability with Microsoft's 'Azure' cloud. It supports creating, updating and deleting registered apps, service principals, users and groups; and can be extended to support other services in 'Graph'.
URL: https://github.com/cloudyr/AzureGraph
BugReports: https://github.com/cloudyr/AzureGraph/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.3)
Imports: 
    AzureAuth,
    utils,
    httr (>= 1.3),
    jsonlite,
    openssl,
    R6
Suggests:
    AzureRMR,
    knitr,
    testthat
